[https://www.tads.org/ TADS 3] is a programming language for creating interactive fiction.  

From the author's site: "TADS is the programmer's power tool for IF authoring. It offers a robust and modern language that'll be instantly familiar to anyone who knows Javascript or C++, and a full-featured suite of development tools from text editing to debugging."


The TADS3-mode for Emacs can be downloaded here: https://github.com/tads-working-group/tads3-mode



